        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-31" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#601414);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);movable=1;resizable=1;rotatable=1;deletable=1;editable=1;locked=0;connectable=1;strokeWidth=3;align=center;fontColor=default;fontSize=30;" value="Critérios de Aceitação" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="310" width="280" x="210" y="230" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-32" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;blockquote style=&quot;margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;1,6,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1,6,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;1,6,1,0&quot;&gt;Média&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="1260" x="491" y="-180" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-33" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,7,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;1. O utilizador encontra-se devidamente autenticado na plataforma.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,7,1,2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;2. O sistema já possui dados acumulados suficientes (registos de assiduidade, eventos de jogo, notas&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;técnicas) para gerar representações estatísticas significativas.&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="150" width="1261" x="490" y="-120" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-34" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;1. O sistema compila os dados da base de dados e renderiza os gráficos e tabelas instantaneamente,&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;ajustados ao nível de acesso do utilizador.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,1,2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;2. Os dados apresentados nestes painéis funcionam em modo de apenas leitura (&lt;i data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,1,2&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;77&quot;&gt;read-only&lt;/i&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="200" width="1260" x="490" y="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-35" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;br&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;1,9,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1,9,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,9,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;1. O sistema tem de garantir o isolamento da informação: um atleta apenas visualiza as suas próprias&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;estatísticas, enquanto o treinador tem uma visão agregada da sua equipa.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,9,1,2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;2. A interface deve permitir filtrar a informação temporalmente (ex: últimos 30 dias, época atual, época&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;transata).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,9,1,4&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;3. A gerência deve ter a possibilidade de exportar os dados globais dos painéis de desempenho para&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;formatos padrão (ex: PDF ou Excel) para apresentação em reuniões de direção ou a potenciais investidores.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="310" width="1260" x="489" y="230" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
