        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-32" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;blockquote style=&quot;margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;1,6,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1,6,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;1,6,1,0&quot;&gt;Média&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="1260" x="491" y="-180" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-33" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,7,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;1. O utilizador criador encontra-se autenticado com o perfil de Treinador.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,7,1,2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;2. O atleta a avaliar está devidamente inscrito e integra o plantel associado a esse treinador.&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="150" width="1261" x="490" y="-120" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-34" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;1. O relatório técnico ou o objetivo é persistido na base de dados, anexado ao processo desportivo do&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;atleta.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,1,2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;2. O atleta (e o seu encarregado de educação) passa a ter acesso de leitura a esta avaliação na sua área&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;pessoal.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,1,4&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;3. O sistema gera uma notificação informando o atleta de que uma nova avaliação ou objetivo foi publicado&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="250" width="1260" x="490" y="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-35" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;1,9,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1,9,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,9,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;1. O formulário de avaliação deve permitir a atribuição de pontuações rápidas (ex: escalas numéricas ou&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;estrelas) e a introdução de notas em texto livre.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,9,1,2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;2. O módulo de objetivos deve permitir definir metas claras com datas limite (&lt;i data-path-to-node=&quot;1,9,1,2&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;78&quot;&gt;deadlines&lt;/i&gt;) e estados de&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;progresso (ex: &quot;Em curso&quot;, &quot;Atingido&quot;, &quot;Não Atingido&quot;).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,9,1,4&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;3. O sistema deve garantir total privacidade, impedindo que um atleta visualize as avaliações técnicas e os&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;objetivos traçados para os seus colegas de equipa.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="310" width="1260" x="489" y="280" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
