        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-33" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,7,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;1. O utilizador encontra-se autenticado na plataforma.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,7,1,2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;2. A integração com os &lt;i data-path-to-node=&quot;1,7,1,2&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;23&quot;&gt;gateways&lt;/i&gt; de pagamento externos (ex: SIBS, Ifthenpay) encontra-se configurada e&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;ativa.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,7,1,4&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;3. O plano de pagamentos (mensalidades, taxas de inscrição, seguros) está previamente definido pela&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;gerência para aquela época e modalidade.&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="260" width="1261" x="490" y="-120" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-34" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;1. Após a confirmação do pagamento, a transação é averbada automaticamente na conta corrente do&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;utilizador.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,1,2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;2. O sistema gera a fatura/recibo em formato PDF e disponibiliza-a para download na área pessoal.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,1,4&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;3. Se o pagamento regularizar uma situação de dívida, o sistema levanta automaticamente eventuais&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;suspensões desportivas aplicadas ao atleta.&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="250" width="1260" x="491" y="140" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-35" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;1,9,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1,9,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,9,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;1. O sistema deve permitir que um perfil parental consolide as quotas de vários educandos (ex: irmãos no&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;futebol e na natação) numa única referência de pagamento mensal.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,9,1,2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;2. O módulo deve aplicar regras de negócio para bloqueio automático (ex: impedir a convocatória de atletas&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;com mais de dois meses de quotas em atraso).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,9,1,4&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;3. A tesouraria deve dispor de uma vista de &quot;Devedores&quot; em tempo real, com a possibilidade de acionar o&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;motor de notificações para enviar lembretes amigáveis de cobrança.&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="310" width="1260" x="490" y="390" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
