        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-31" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#330000);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);movable=1;resizable=1;rotatable=1;deletable=1;editable=1;locked=0;connectable=1;strokeWidth=3;align=center;fontColor=default;fontSize=30;" value="Critério de Verificação" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="290" width="280" x="211" y="-180" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-32" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;blockquote style=&quot;margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;1,5,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1,5,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;1,5,1,0&quot;&gt;Média&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="1260" x="491" y="-240" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-35" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;1,9,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1,9,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,6,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;1. O sistema deve suportar, no mínimo, 100 utilizadores em sessões ativas simultâneas sem interrupção de&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;serviço.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,6,1,2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;2. A base de dados deve estar otimizada com índices adequados para garantir que o aumento do volume&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;de registos (ex: milhares de presenças ao longo dos anos) não torne as consultas mais lentas.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,6,1,4&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;3. A infraestrutura de servidor (Cloud) deve permitir o escalonamento vertical ou horizontal de recursos de&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;forma rápida em caso de necessidade.&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="290" width="1260" x="491" y="-180" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
